description: Robert Duvall gives an amazing performance as a Marine fighter pilot who funnels his frustrated desire to fight into creating a tip-top battalion out of his own emotionally battered family. This critically acclaimed movie has become a touchstone for dysfunctional families and is based on the Pat Conroy novel.
